 * a non-scalar can never get in — the compiler rejects it, no runtime guard
 * needed. Arrays and objects are not scalar; for those, reach for a plain
 * {@see Option} or a {@see Union}.
 *
 * Generated by code-commandments — safe to edit.
 *
 * @code-commandments-generated
 */
final class ScalarOption
